00:09:28.746 --> 00:09:31.750
menghabiskan waktu bersama

00:09:31.980 --> 00:09:33.511
di bawah satu ruangan

00:09:33.570 --> 00:09:35.403
di bawah satu atap

00:09:36.917 --> 00:09:40.947
prioritas mereka berubah.

00:09:42.117 --> 00:09:43.578
